[python script to exe file - py2exe]
1. install py2exe-0.6.9
2. create setup_centos_utility.py
3. python setup_centos_utility.py py2exe

[python script to exe file - pyinstaller]
1. download pyinstaller , https://github.com/pyinstaller/pyinstaller/releases/download/v3.2.1/PyInstaller-3.2.1.zip
2. install pyinstaller , python setup.py install
3. back to directory of pyinstaller
4. execute command, python pyinstaller.py -F -w centos_utility.py

